    "body" : "<pre><code>// check if ch is a letter\nif ((ch &gt;= 'a' &amp;&amp; ch &lt;= 'z') || (ch &gt;= 'A' &amp;&amp; ch &lt;= 'Z'))\n    // ...\n\n// check if ch is a digit\nif (ch &gt;= '0' &amp;&amp; ch &lt;= '9')\n    // ...\n\n// check if ch is a whitespace\nif ((ch == ' ') || (ch =='\\n') || (ch == '\\t'))\n    // ...\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/i18n/text/charintro.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/i18n/text/charintro.html</a></p>\n"
